This template builds an alternative form of [[common fraction]]s. It takes one, two or three parameters: the optional integer (may be signed), the optional numerator and the required denominator; in this order. Please '''do not''' substitute it.

; <code><nowiki>{{sfrac|A|B|C}}</nowiki></code>
: {{sfrac|A|B|C}} (integer, numerator and denominator)
; <code><nowiki>{{sfrac|A|B}}</nowiki></code>
: {{sfrac|A|B}} (numerator and denominator)
; <code><nowiki>{{sfrac|A}}</nowiki></code>
: {{sfrac|A}} (denominator only)

